:markdown
  The mobile menu allows you to navigate the
  contents of an app on small viewports. It represents the
  navigation as a hierarchy.
  
  It is usually hidden in a drawer-like component that slides
  in with the tap onto a burger icon. However, that functionality
  is part of the [Site Component](/components/site.html "Site Component").

