  # Sliding Mobile Menu
  
  The sliding mobile menu only shows one level of hierarchy
  at a time. It transitions between levels by sliding to the left
  or right side.
  
  When deeper than the highest level, the uppermost item
  tells the user which level he's in. Clicking that item
  transitions back to the parent level.

