          :markdown
            If you omit the `data-menu="sliding"` attribute, the
            menu won't get any functionality.
            
            In order to add
            the missing functionality programmatically, simply initialize the
            `$().slidingMenu()` plugin.
            
            ```js
            var menu = $("[data-menu='sliding']")
            
            // initialize the plugin
            menu.slidingMenu()
            ```
            
            The plugin you activated provides the `level` method which
            allows you to get or set the current level that is displayed
            in the menu.
            
            ```js
            // get the current level as a jQuery node
            var level = menu.slidingMenu('level')
            
            // navigate to another level
            
            // set level to the previously saved one
            menu.slidingMenu('level', level)
            ```

